name: Apo Diver
description: Apo Diver is a dive center in San Juan, Siquijor, Philippines. Dive and snorkel trips around the island of Siquijor are organised on a daily basis. Snorkel and scuba diving gear rental is also available. Guests can additionally enjoy the pool and bar as well as direct access to the beach before and after day trips. We're looking forward to welcoming you to Siquijor!
address: Siquijor Circumferential Road San Juan Solangon Beach, Siquijor 6227 Philippines
